id: pm-bwyw
title: "As a long-lived agent returning to a workspace after an hour or a year, pm context restores my working memory — active work, why it matters, distilled learnings, and what changed while I was away — in bounded tokens"
description: "Time-dimension continuity story completing the spectrum trio: pm-g2zz covers workspace scale, pm-z436 the small end, this covers gap length. End-to-end acceptance narrative for the composed context engine (ADR pm-vvib). Dedupe-checked: no existing resumption/continuity story."
